## Key Industry Developments
* April 2023 – BAJAJ launched its new ceiling-mounted fans collection.
* August 2022 – Orient Electric unveiled its smart ceiling fan, Orient Aeroslim.
* June 2022 – Goldmedal Electricals introduced its new decorative ceiling-mounted fan, Insignia.
* September 2021 - Panasonic Corporation opened its new manufacturing facility in Binh Duong, Vietnam.

